<div class="border-top" style="width: 100%; max-width: 50%; margin-top: 15px"></div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="border-top generic-devider-line" style="margin-top: -1px;"></div>
    <div class="py-2"></div>
    <h3>Info</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">
        <strong>Grade Master</strong> is a grade management tool that helps you manage your education, subjects, and grades.
        <br/><br/>
        <strong>Official Repository:</strong>
        <a class="btn-link" href="https://github.com/DevT06/GradeMaster" target="_blank">GitHub - DevT06/GradeMaster</a>
        <br/><br/>
        <strong>Version Information:</strong>
    </p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
        - <strong>Installed Version:</strong> <span id="installedVersion">2.2.0</span>
        <span id="currentInstalledVersion" class="alert alert-secondary" style="padding: 2px 5px">
