        </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
        - <strong>Latest Available Version:</strong>
        <a id="latestAvailableVersion" class="alert alert-primary" style="padding: 2px 5px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://github.com/DevT06/GradeMaster/releases" target="_blank">
            Checking...
        </a>
    </p>
    <p>
        - <strong>Client Version:</strong> GradeMaster.DesktopClient - 2.2.0.1
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top: 50px;"></div>

    <img src="images/logo.png" alt="GradeMaster Logo" style="max-width: 200px;"/>
    <h4 style="font-size: 26px;">Grade Master</h4>
</div>

<script>
    window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'auto' });
    window.checkForUpdates();
</script>

